1448
01:38:50,490 --> 01:38:53,516
<i>They're going for the all-time
American League record...</i>

1449
01:38:53,727 --> 01:38:54,785
<i>...20 games in a row.</i>

1450
01:38:54,995 --> 01:38:55,984
<i>We're going to 20!</i>

1451
01:38:56,196 --> 01:38:59,256
<i>We're gonna take the AL record
