01:41:37,557 --> 01:41:40,492
<i>Now batting, number 18...</i>

1489
01:41:40,694 --> 01:41:44,824
<i>...left fielder Raúl Ibañez.</i>

1490
01:42:46,026 --> 01:42:47,584
Safe.

1491
01:42:50,030 --> 01:42:52,396
<i>And the A's now lead by a score
of 11 to 3.</i>

1492
01:42:52,599 --> 01:42:55,363
<i>A nice cushion,
but you don't wanna give teams life...</i>

1493
01:42:55,568 --> 01:42:59,470
<i>...and let them wedge their way
