01:44:23,523 --> 01:44:26,458
<i>Two out. Runners at first and third.</i>

1505
01:44:26,659 --> 01:44:29,093
<i>And the 3-2 delivery.</i>

1506
01:45:02,896 --> 01:45:05,160
<i>It's weird, Billy.</i>

1507
01:45:05,365 --> 01:45:09,392
<i>You wanna give up baseball
