1536
01:48:36,909 --> 01:48:38,877
<i>How do you explain it?</i>

1537
01:48:39,879 --> 01:48:44,179
<i>Crazy. Just plain crazy.</i>

1538
01:48:48,321 --> 01:48:51,848
<i>Hatteberg is mobbed at home plate.</i>

1539
01:48:55,128 --> 01:48:58,063
<i>In 103 years
of American League baseball...</i>

1540
01:48:58,264 --> 01:49:01,700
<i>...the Athletics have accomplished
what no one has before.</i>

1541
01:49:01,901 --> 01:49:06,099
<i>They have won
20 consecutive games.</i>

1542
01:49:32,131 --> 01:49:34,895
<i>It's hard not to be romantic
