1544
01:49:40,973 --> 01:49:44,374
<i>It sells tickets and hot dogs.</i>

1545
01:49:45,711 --> 01:49:47,269
<i>Doesn't mean anything.</i>

1546
01:49:47,480 --> 01:49:51,075
<i>Billy, we just won 20 games
