1572
01:51:35,288 --> 01:51:37,756
<i>...and went nowhere
after losing three straight.</i>

1573
01:51:37,957 --> 01:51:41,222
<i>With a win today over the Twins,
Oakland moves into the ALCS...</i>

1574
01:51:41,427 --> 01:51:44,760
